Advanced Taglist
------------------------------------

******** PLEASE DO NOT USE THIS EXTENSION YET. IT'S NOT READY!! ***********







Version: 1.0
Author: Alistair Kearney (alistair@symphony21.com)
Build Date: 22nd Jan 2009
Requirements: Latest Symphony 2 build

Replacement for the standard taglist field in Symphony. Includes a limiting value to prevent suggestions
from becoming too many, and sorting options.

[INSTALLATION]

1. Upload the 'advancedtaglist' folder in this archive to your Symphony 'extensions' folder.

2. Enable it by selecting the "Advanced Taglist", choose Enable from the with-selected menu, then click Apply.

3. Add the "Advanced Taglist" field to your sections
